Global Sodium Iodate Market Insights
Sodium Iodate Market size was valued at USD 0.50 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.75 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Sodium Iodate Market Overview
The global sodium iodate market size is valued at USD 1.2 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 1.6 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% during the forecast period. Sodium iodate is extensively used in the pharmaceutical, food & beverage, and industrial sectors, providing a broad range of applications. In pharmaceuticals, it serves as a reagent in the manufacture of iodine-based medicines, while in food & beverage, it is used as a nutrient supplement. Increasing demand from these industries, along with the growing need for iodine compounds, is a major driver behind the market's growth.

